ci_support_linux_64_is_freethreadingfals:
c_compiler:
- gcc
c_compiler_version:
- '14'
c_stdlib:
- sysroot
c_stdlib_version:
- '2.17'
channel_sources:
- conda-forge
channel_targets:
- conda-forge main
cxx_compiler:
- gxx
cxx_compiler_version:
- '14'
docker_image:
- quay.io/condaforge/linux-anvil-x86_64:alma9
is_freethreading:
- false
numpy:
- '2'
pin_run_as_build:
  python:
    min_pin: x.x
    max_pin: x.x
python:
- 3.11.* *_cpython
target_platform:
- linux-64
zip_keys:
- - c_compiler_version
  - cxx_compiler_version
- - python
  - is_freethreading
name: geoana
raw_meta_yaml:
context:
  version: "0.8.1"
  # ensure is_freethreading gets detected as a used variable
  touch_is_freethreading: ${{ is_freethreading }}

package:
  name: geoana
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/g/geoana/geoana-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 20fb32b805827e4fef3eb5f41f95c9b606433681a8a2339d19416a2bfec5f76f

build:
  number: 0
  skip: match(python, "<3.11") or (match(python, "=3.14") and linux and is_freethreading and (aarch64 or ppc64le))

requirements:
  build:
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - python
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - cython
        - numpy
        - ninja
        - pkg-config
        - meson-python
    - ${{ stdlib('c') }}
    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - meson-python
    - ninja
    - pkg-config
    - python
    - python-build
    - cython
    - numpy
    - setuptools_scm >=6.2
  run:
    - python
    - numpy >=1.22
    - scipy >=1.12
    - libdlf

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - geoana
        - geoana.earthquake
        - geoana.em
        - geoana.kernels._extensions

about:
  homepage: https://www.simpeg.xyz
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Interactive geoscience (mostly) analytic functions.
  repository: https://github.com/simpeg/geoana
  documentation: https://geoana.simpeg.xyz

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lheagy
    - jcapriot
